        <abstract>
            <p>Will finish last chapter (except recapitulation) tomorrow.</p>
            <p>Pleased with JDH’s response to geographical distribution chapter;</p>
            <p>CD disagrees with Lyell’s view that glacial epoch is connected with position of continents.</p>
        </abstract>
